      • setReduceOnSourceId

        public EdgeTargetDegree<K,VV,EV> setReduceOnSourceId(boolean reduceOnSourceId)
        The degree can be counted from either the edge source or target IDs. By default the target IDs are counted. Reducing on source IDs may optimize the algorithm if the input edge list is sorted by source ID.
        参数:
        reduceOnSourceId - set to true if the input edge list is sorted by target ID
        返回:
        this
